UPDATE tours SET translations = '{"ko":{"title":"제주 겨울 감귤·설경·동백 소그룹 투어","description":"한라산 어리목 트레일(겨울 설경), 감귤(귤) 따기 체험(겨울 할라봉 절정), 카멜리아힐(동백꽃 절정), 대포주상절리(유네스코), 천제연폭포를 포함한 제주 겨울 한정 소그룹 투어.","badges":["소그룹","제주","겨울 한정","시즌 한정","감귤 따기","동백꽃","설경"],"duration":"9 hours"},"ja":{"title":"済州冬ツアー：みかん・雪・山茶花（南西部）","description":"冬の済州（12〜2月）にしか体験できない3大テーマで組んだ南西部日帰りツアー：漢拏山御利目コースの樹氷林ハイク・カメリアヒルの満開の山茶花（冬がピーク）・ハルラボンのみかん狩り体験。さらに大浦柱状節理と天帝淵の滝も。","badges":["冬限定","済州","みかん狩り","山茶花","漢拏山"],"duration":"冬限定（一日ツアー）"},"zh":{"title":"济州冬季西南路线：橘子采摘、雪景＆山茶花一日游","description":"A seasonal winter day-tour of southwest Jeju (December through February) built around the three things only Jeju does well in winter: snow on Hallasan''s slopes, red camellias in full bloom at Camellia Hill, and pick-your-own Jeju tangerines (gyul) at a working orchard. The route also covers Cheonjeyeon Falls, Jusangjeolli columnar cliffs, and the Osulloc Tea Museum. Hotel pickup in Jeju City, English/Chinese-speaking licensed guide.","badges":["小团体","济州","冬季限定","季节限定","橘子采摘","山茶花","雪景"],"duration":"9 hours"},"zh-TW":{"title":"濟州冬季西南路線：橘子採摘、雪景＆山茶花一日遊","description":"A seasonal winter day-tour of southwest Jeju (December through February) built around the three things only Jeju does well in winter: snow on Hallasan''s slopes, red camellias in full bloom at Camellia Hill, and pick-your-own Jeju tangerines (gyul) at a working orchard. The route also covers Cheonjeyeon Falls, Jusangjeolli columnar cliffs, and the Osulloc Tea Museum. Hotel pickup in Jeju City, English/Chinese-speaking licensed guide.","badges":["小團體","濟州","冬季限定","季節限定","橘子採摘","山茶花","雪景"],"duration":"9 hours"},"es":{"title":"Tour Invierno Jeju Suroeste: Nieve en el Hallasan, Recogida de Mandarinas y Camelias","description":"Las tres experiencias únicas del invierno de Jeju en un día: senderismo en el sendero nevado Eorimok del Hallasan (árboles cubiertos de escarcha y nieve en la montaña más alta de Corea) → recogida de mandarinas Hallabong de invierno en una granja local → almuerzo → Camellia Hill (las camelias rojas en su pico de diciembre-enero) → Acantilado Jusangjeolli → Cascadas Cheonjeyeon. Diciembre-febrero, grupo pequeño, recogida en hotel.","badges":["Solo invierno","Nieve + mandarinas + camelias","Grupo pequeño","Recogida en hotel"],"duration":"Un día (dic-feb)"}}'::jsonb, updated_at = NOW() WHERE slug = 'jeju-winter-southwest-tangerine-snow-camellia-tour';
UPDATE tours SET translations = '{"ko":{"title":"포천 산정호수·허브아일랜드·아트밸리 소그룹 투어","description":"산정호수(명성산·철봉산 품은 고산 호수, 4km 산책로), 포천 허브아일랜드(약 8만2,000㎡ 지중해 테마 허브 정원), 포천 아트밸리(1970년대 화강암 채석장 → 예술 공원, 조각공원+천주호)를 소그룹으로.","badges":["자연·사진 투어","시즌 하이라이트","낭만 야경"],"duration":"10 hours"},"ja":{"title":"抱川日帰りツアー：山正湖・ハーブアイランド・アートバレー","description":"ソウルから約1時間の京畿道・抱川市への少人数日帰りツアー。「韓国のプロヴァンス」とも呼ばれる山に囲まれた山正湖→200種以上のハーブが咲く抱川ハーブアイランド（10万平米）→廃採石場を再活用した野外彫刻公園・抱川アートバレー（チョンジュ湖が見どころ）。","badges":["ソウル発","抱川","ハーブアイランド","アートバレー","自然＆アート"],"duration":"一日ツアー"},"zh":{"title":"抱川一日游：山亭湖、香草岛＆抱川艺术谷","description":"A relaxed seasonal day-trip from Seoul to Pocheon, the Gyeonggi countryside known for its lakes, herb gardens, and dramatic art-park landscapes. The route combines Sanjeong Lake''s mountain-circled waters, Herb Island''s Mediterranean-style gardens and evening lights, and Pocheon Art Valley''s monorail-accessed quarry observatory. Less crowded than Nami Island and built around photo-led calm rather than landmark sprint.","badges":["自然摄影之旅","季节精华","浪漫夜灯"],"duration":"10 hours"},"zh-TW":{"title":"抱川一日遊：山亭湖、香草島＆抱川藝術谷","description":"A relaxed seasonal day-trip from Seoul to Pocheon, the Gyeonggi countryside known for its lakes, herb gardens, and dramatic art-park landscapes. The route combines Sanjeong Lake''s mountain-circled waters, Herb Island''s Mediterranean-style gardens and evening lights, and Pocheon Art Valley''s monorail-accessed quarry observatory. Less crowded than Nami Island and built around photo-led calm rather than landmark sprint.","badges":["自然攝影之旅","季節精華","浪漫夜燈"],"duration":"10 hours"},"es":{"title":"Pocheon Day Trip: Sanjeong Lake, Herb Island & Pocheon Art Valley","description":"Excursión de un día desde Seúl a Pocheon, a ~1 hora al norte: el Lago Sanjeong (paisaje alpino de montaña a 380 m) → Herb Island de Pocheon (10 ha de jardines aromáticos, apodado el Provence de Corea, más de 100 especies) → Arte Valle de Pocheon (antigua cantera de granito reconvertida en parque escultórico con el lago Cheonju de color esmeralda). Tres escenas radicalmente distintas en un día.","badges":["Nature & Photo Trip","Seasonal Highlights","Romantic Evening Lights"],"duration":"10 hours"}}'::jsonb, updated_at = NOW() WHERE slug = 'pocheon-sanjeong-lake-herb-island-art-valley';
UPDATE tours SET translations = '{"ko":{"title":"서울 DMZ 프라이빗 투어: 제3땅굴+감악산 출렁다리","description":"임진각 평화공원, 제3땅굴(1978년 발견 북한 침투 터널), 도라전망대(판문점 방향 DMZ 조망), 감악산 출렁다리(220m 현수교)를 프라이빗으로 하루에. 여권 지참 필수. 월요일 미운행.","badges":["프라이빗 전세 투어","DMZ+출렁다리","호텔 픽업 포함"],"duration":"8–9 hours"},"ja":{"title":"ソウルDMZプライベートツアー：第3トンネル＆駒岳山レッドブリッジ","description":"韓国で最も重い歴史的スポットとフォトジェニックな山の吊り橋を組み合わせたプライベート日帰りツアー。午前は非武装地帯（臨津閣平和公園→第3浸透トンネル→都羅展望台）、午後は駒岳山の鮮やかな赤いサスペンションブリッジへ。パスポート必携。","badges":["プライベート","DMZ","第3トンネル","ソウル発","パスポート必須"],"duration":"一日ツアー"},"zh":{"title":"首尔DMZ私人行程：第三地道＆감악산悬索桥","description":"A private day-trip pairing Korea''s heaviest historical site with one of its most photogenic mountain bridges. Morning at the DMZ (Imjingak Peace Park, 3rd Infiltration Tunnel, Dora Observatory), then an afternoon walk across the 220-meter Gamaksan Red Suspension Bridge. Passport required for the DMZ portion.","badges":["私人包车游","非军事区＋悬索桥","饭店接送含括"],"duration":"8–9 hours"},"zh-TW":{"title":"首爾DMZ私人行程：第三地道＆감악산懸索橋","description":"A private day-trip pairing Korea''s heaviest historical site with one of its most photogenic mountain bridges. Morning at the DMZ (Imjingak Peace Park, 3rd Infiltration Tunnel, Dora Observatory), then an afternoon walk across the 220-meter Gamaksan Red Suspension Bridge. Passport required for the DMZ portion.","badges":["私人包車遊","非軍事區＋懸索橋","飯店接送含括"],"duration":"8–9 hours"},"es":{"title":"Seoul DMZ Private Tour: 3rd Tunnel + Gamaksan Suspension Bridge","description":"Tour privado al DMZ (Zona Desmilitarizada) desde Seúl con recogida en hotel: Parque de la Paz de Imjingak (Puente de la Libertad de 1953) → 3er Túnel de Infiltración (descubierto en 1978, a 44 km de Seúl, ⚠️ pasaporte obligatorio) → Observatorio Dora (punto de observación más septentrional de Corea del Sur) → Puente colgante rojo de Gamaksan (150 m sobre el barranco). Coche privado, recogida en hotel.","badges":["Private Tour","DMZ + Suspension Bridge","Hotel Pickup Included"],"duration":"8–9 hours"}}'::jsonb, updated_at = NOW() WHERE slug = 'seoul-dmz-private-3rd-tunnel-suspension-bridge';
UPDATE tours SET translations = '{"ko":{"title":"서울 프라이빗 투어: 남이섬·아침고요수목원·쁘띠프랑스","description":"남이섬(460,000㎡ 강 섬, 페리 도착), 아침고요수목원(한국 대표 사립 수목원), 쁘띠프랑스(프랑스 테마 문화 마을)를 프라이빗 차량으로 하루에. 전 입장료 포함.","badges":["프라이빗 전세 투어","한드 촬영지","커플·가족 추천"],"duration":"9–10 hours"},"ja":{"title":"ソウルプライベートツアー：南怡島・晨靜苑・プチフランス","description":"「冬のソナタ」のロケ地・南怡島の並木フェリー体験、22のテーマ庭園を持つ晨靜苑の花の散策、「星の王子さま」がテーマのプチフランスのコロニアル建築街を巡るソウル発プライベート日帰りツアー。ホテル送迎・全入場料込み。","badges":["プライベート","南怡島","晨靜苑","プチフランス","ソウル発"],"duration":"一日ツアー（プライベート）"},"zh":{"title":"首尔私人行程：南怡岛、晨静苑＆小法国村","description":"A private day trip from Seoul covering Nami Island''s tree-lined ferry experience, the Garden of Morning Calm''s themed garden walks, and the colorful Le Petit Prince village of Petite France. Hotel pickup, private vehicle, and a relaxed pace make this the comfort-led version of a classic Gapyeong loop.","badges":["私人包车游","韩剧拍摄地","情侣家庭适合"],"duration":"9–10 hours"},"zh-TW":{"title":"首爾私人行程：南怡島、晨靜苑＆小法國村","description":"A private day trip from Seoul covering Nami Island''s tree-lined ferry experience, the Garden of Morning Calm''s themed garden walks, and the colorful Le Petit Prince village of Petite France. Hotel pickup, private vehicle, and a relaxed pace make this the comfort-led version of a classic Gapyeong loop.","badges":["私人包車遊","韓劇拍攝地","情侶家庭適合"],"duration":"9–10 hours"},"es":{"title":"Tour Privado Seúl→Gapyeong: Isla Nami, Jardín de la Mañana Tranquila y Petite France","description":"Las tres experiencias más fotogénicas de Gapyeong en un día privado desde Seúl: Isla Nami (isla fluvial, ''Winter Sonata'', arboleda de metasecoya) → Jardín de la Mañana Tranquila (330.000 m², 22 jardines temáticos) → Petite France (aldea alsaciana con la mayor colección de ''El Principito'' de Asia). Coche privado, recogida en hotel, entradas incluidas.","badges":["Tour privado","Isla Nami","K-drama","Parejas y familias"],"duration":"Un día privado"}}'::jsonb, updated_at = NOW() WHERE slug = 'seoul-private-nami-morning-calm-petite-france';
UPDATE tours SET translations = '{"ko":{"title":"서울 출발 설악산·속초해변 일일 투어","description":"설악산국립공원(유네스코 생물권보전지역, 신흥사, 케이블카 선택), 속초관광수산시장(동해 해산물), 속초해변을 소그룹으로 하루에. 서울 왕복 차량 포함.","badges":["소그룹","자연 경관","절경","해변","수산시장","단풍","일일 투어"],"duration":"12 hours"},"ja":{"title":"雪岳山国立公園＆束草海岸日帰りツアー（ソウル発）","description":"韓国で最も愛される山岳国立公園と東海岸の港町・束草を巡るソウル発少人数日帰りツアー。雪岳山の花崗岩峰・渓谷・新興寺と青銅大仏（ケーブルカーで標高800mへ）に、束草の活きの良い海産物市場と白砂ビーチを組み合わせた14〜16時間の充実コース。","badges":["ソウル発","雪岳山","束草","国立公園","東海岸"],"duration":"一日ツアー（約14〜16時間）"},"zh":{"title":"首尔出发雪岳山国立公园＆束草海滩一日游","description":"A small-group day-trip from Seoul to Korea''s most-loved national park and the East Sea coastal city of Sokcho. The route pairs Seoraksan''s granite peaks, valleys, and Buddhist heritage with the seafood market and beach of Sokcho — a mountain-and-ocean combination only the east coast offers. 12 hours with English-speaking guide and round-trip transport.","badges":["小团体","自然风光","绝美景色","海滩","海鲜市场","Autumn Foliage","一日游"],"duration":"12 hours"},"zh-TW":{"title":"首爾出發雪嶽山國立公園＆束草海灘一日遊","description":"A small-group day-trip from Seoul to Korea''s most-loved national park and the East Sea coastal city of Sokcho. The route pairs Seoraksan''s granite peaks, valleys, and Buddhist heritage with the seafood market and beach of Sokcho — a mountain-and-ocean combination only the east coast offers. 12 hours with English-speaking guide and round-trip transport.","badges":["小團體","自然風光","絕美景色","海灘","海鮮市場","Autumn Foliage","一日遊"],"duration":"12 hours"},"es":{"title":"Tour Seúl→Seoraksan: Parque Nacional UNESCO, Mercado de Sokcho y Playa","description":"Excursión intensa de un día desde Seúl al Parque Nacional Seoraksan (Reserva de la Biosfera UNESCO, las montañas de granito más espectaculares de Corea) y la ciudad costera de Sokcho: cablecar hasta los 800 m + Templo Sinheungsa y Buda de Bronce → Mercado Pesquero de Sokcho (marisco de primera mano) → Playa de Sokcho (Mar del Este, arena blanca). 14-16 horas de ida y vuelta. Solo para quien quiera una jornada intensa.","badges":["Grupo pequeño","Naturaleza","Seoraksan UNESCO","Playa","Mercado marisco","Follaje otoñal","Excursión un día"],"duration":"14-16 horas (jornada intensa)"}}'::jsonb, updated_at = NOW() WHERE slug = 'seoul-seoraksan-national-park-sokcho-beach-day-trip';
